Audiffex -AmpLion PRO v1.1.3 [deepstatus]

AmpLion turns your computer into an ultimate guitar stack. Use it in standalone mode for playing live, learning and rehearsing or as a plug-in module to enhance your guitar tracks.

AmpLion features ultra-precise simulation of 9 guitar preamps, 7 power amps, 12 speakers, 8 microphones and 30 effects deliver extra wide variety of unique guitar sounds.
Compatibility

Standalone application, VST 2.4, RTAS, AU (Mac only), AAX
Requirements

PC: CPU with SSE2 support (Intel Pentium 4 or AMD Athlon 64 and newer), Windows Vista, 7, 8 (32-bit/64-bit), ASIO compatible audio interface
